name: Queer Meet and Greet - Meetup
description:
This is a queer meet and greet event hosted by Prarthana (@shorthairedbrownqueer). It's an informal, inclusive and neurodivergent friendly space for members of the LGBTQIA+ to come together and connect with like-minded folks.
Folks of all ages from the LGBTQIA+ community are welcome!

name: Beat by Beat - Music Based Wellness Workshop
description:
🎶 Beat by Beat 🎶
End the year with rhythm, reflection, and self-discovery!
Join two coaches and a talented music facilitator for a fun, reflective musical program designed to spark self-discovery and celebration. Dive into the rhythm of growth and step into the new year with renewed energy and clarity.
No music skills required—just bring your curiosity and energy!
✨ Limited spots available—confirm yours now✨
